metadata.name: FACADE
metadata.description:
FACADE

The word implies: 
Deceptive outward appearance

We often represent ourselves in a befitting way to the world; behind that mask lies a universe of regrets, worries and pain.

This helmet represents the FACADE we all showcase to different extents to fit into society.

The scenery outside the window represents our colourful lives which we don't acknowledge or enjoy the present moments due to this helmet of a facade that doesn't allow us to break free.

To absorb the good and the positivity around us requires us all to break our  "Helmets Of Rumination"

FPS: 30
Dimensions: 1600*3200px

NOTE: Collector of the artwork can request an un-compressed 2000*4000px MP4.
